{"tid":2518520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣布放棄mRNA新冠疫苗知識產權，A股後星醫藥、康希諾-U今日大跌","createTime":"2021-05-06T05:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:47:38.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d223a9925f173eab9a4f1f86e17937001dc2ad6f","tid":2518520,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"5月6日消息，中國多隻疫苗概念股大跌。其中，複星醫藥A股一度跌停，康希諾-U也一度大跌超15%。<br />\n<br />\n消息面上，此前南非和印度向世貿組織要求美國放棄疫苗相關專利。美當地時間5月5日，拜登政府改變之前態度，表示美國將支持放棄相關專利。<br />\n<br />\n不過對于上述動作，中國部分券商對此並未表現出悲觀態度。東興證券稱，美國放棄mRNA新冠疫苗知識產權不影響當前緊缺狀況。<br />\n<br />\n海通證券也認為，mRNA疫苗的核心壁壘之一在于遞送系統，即使此次專利放棄最終實現，也只會是對mRNA序列專利的放棄，影響有限。此外，mRNA生產技術仍具有壁壘，短期內難以被其他藥企完全掌握。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSowcR9et6dTs6AdUzGeT3daS87J7nricuHF5QXygbcyV?filename=Hm63NHd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHm63NHd.jpg&h=9585618b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmemo6kzV8iY8suyErKP1oDM4ngLzujwvPJW8FxgVyjjKi?filename=4gOd9VB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gOd9VB.jpg&h=c8a83ad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f9b3313ac4d496577d61bb3a1238f316a454a7f","tid":2518520,"uid":349058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"連登仔：宜家唔打遲d無哂疫苗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a2c15727b0d2642e2712c262929b1978d81f05","tid":2518520,"uid":308595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"支國可大量生產唔合格嘅疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34eb4962d05664710505a64de770017e0c922723","tid":2518520,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"你有password<br />\n但係無decode部機，都係無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a